# Resend API key — required for contact form submissions.
# 1. Sign up at https://resend.com (free tier: 100 emails/day, 3,000/mo)
# 2. Create an API key in the dashboard
# 3. Copy it here as RESEND_API_KEY
# 4. Save this file as `.env.local` (without the .example suffix)
#
# Until a custom domain is verified in Resend, the app sends from
# `onboarding@resend.dev`. With the free tier and that sender, Resend
# will only deliver to the email address used to register the Resend
# account — sign up using makaturaorlando@gmail.com so the form works
# out of the box. Once a domain is verified, set CONTACT_FROM below.

RESEND_API_KEY=

# Optional: override the From: header once a domain is verified in Resend.
# Example: CONTACT_FROM="The Fightin' Tenth <noreply@thefightintenth.com>"
# CONTACT_FROM=
